profile:
When working with M&M for painting you are getting precise, efficient, and versatile work. We works with various requests and deadlines, making no two jobs the same. We maintain our painting equipment to ensure proper performance and giving the best quality work. M&M has high-quality standards to reduce defects and exceed basic standards at acceptable cost

When doing drywall with M&M measures, cuts, and fits drywall sheets for installation on walls and ceilings, securing them to wooden studs. We add drywall compound and corner beads to fill in joints, screws, and nails to smooth out any imperfections. M&M is comfortable using hand and power tools for sanding and plastering panels and climbing up tall heights.
